                                    "LineChart": {
                                        "Query": "Perf | where ObjectName == \"Memory\" and CounterName == \"% Used Memory\" | summarize Mem = avg(CounterValue) by bin(TimeGenerated, 5m), Computer | sort by TimeGenerated desc\r\n// Oql: Type=Perf ObjectName:Memory CounterName:\"% Used Memory\" | Measure Avg(CounterValue) as Mem by Computer Interval 5MINUTES",
